title: Episode 8 - Trisha Paytas
description:
Dave and Josh recap last weeks mixup with Bryce Hall, and issue another invite for him to join the pod. Trisha Paytas joins to discuss her beef with the D'Amelios, and cancel half of TikTok. Plus another edition of everyones favorite game "Zoomer or Boomer".


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/bffspod
